<div id="review_2264919085" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2264919085" />
    <a title="Michael Ferro" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6105365-michael-ferro"><img alt="Michael Ferro" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1509421150p2/6105365.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2264919085?book_show_action=true">Jan 19, 2018</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Michael Ferro" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Michael Ferro" href="/user/show/6105365-michael-ferro">Michael Ferro</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2264919085" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8712853415470583610">It&apos;s sad how timely and necessary this book is, but that&apos;s modern America. We live in a broken country gone hog wild on greed. A book like this can help change that. No matter your politics, fascism and authoritarianism arise when we&apos;re looking another way, distracted, numb to history. The only way to get out in front of and stop a tyrant is to know what we&apos;re looking for. A book like this can save our country and unite us toward a common goal of change, of striving for democracy, and protect us</span>
  <span id="freeText8712853415470583610" style="display:none">It's sad how timely and necessary this book is, but that's modern America. We live in a broken country gone hog wild on greed. A book like this can help change that. No matter your politics, fascism and authoritarianism arise when we're looking another way, distracted, numb to history. The only way to get out in front of and stop a tyrant is to know what we're looking for. A book like this can save our country and unite us toward a common goal of change, of striving for democracy, and protect us from the dangers of our own rotten impulses. <br /><br />If you only read one book in 2018 (and boy, I hope that's not the case), make it this one. </span>
