<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21878184-the-myth-of-race"><img alt="The Myth of Race: The Troubling Persistence of an Unscientific Idea" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1407112110l/21878184._SX98_.jpg" />
